event_details.description: Merci the Mad Wizard is trying to find true love, and what better way then with some random potion concocting? I'm sure it's perfectly safe and no demonic hordes will be summoned at all.

details.shop_desc: Each Valentines Jeweled Chest contains five cards: two are guaranteed to be gear for the four Event Crusaders (at least one of which will be rare or better); two are random trinkets; one is a time warp card. Chests will weight their gear drops towards unfilled slots and upgrades. Gear will only appear for Warwick and Katie if you have unlocked those Crusaders.
